text: Sphingomonas hankookensis is a Gram-negative, rod-shaped and non-motile bacteria from the genus of Sphingomonas which has been isolated from wastewater from a wastewater treatment plant in Taejon in Korea.Deutsche Sammlung von Mikroorganismen und Zellkulturen UniProt == Further reading == * == References == ==External links== *Type strain of Sphingomonas hankookensis at BacDive - the Bacterial Diversity Metadatabase hankookensis Category:Bacteria described in 2009
title: Sphingomonas hankookensis
